lead_paragraph: Rafael Marquez headed in a late winner to secure Mexico's dramatic 2-1 victory over the United States in a CONCACAF World Cup qualifier match in Ohio on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Late Marquez Header Earns Mexico's Dramatic Win
